snippet.title: Destiny Star Girlfriend 3 OP Movie
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2361750?utm_source=youtubeen

In the final(?) route of this award-winning VN series, Seiji survives an attempt on his life by Kanoko, aka secret magical girl no. 3. The leads all point to a childhood tragedy and a certain deep-space Majin, so why him? And will Kanoko leave the dark side to save Seiji—and mankind—from herself?
